eaway\/individually packaged meals<\/li>\n<li>Hot box food delivery<\/li>\n<li>Contactless food delivery<\/li>\n<li>Extra hygiene measures for staff, facilities and vehicles<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><em>If you\u2019d like a copy of our COVID-19 policy document, please <a href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/contact-us\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">get in touch<\/a>.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We\u2019ve adapted to a new way of catering since COVID and now provide packaged meals and contactless hot box food delivery.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":13886,"featured_media":9743,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[326,33,45,29,340,11],"tags":[347,315,346,323,342,341,343,348,307,345,344],"class_list":["post-9741","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-coronavirus","category-corporate","category-crew","category-film-tv-location","category-hot-box-catering","category-latest-blog-postings","tag-contactless-food-delivery","tag-coronavirus","tag-covid-safe","tag-food-delivery","tag-hot-box","tag-hot-box-catering","tag-hot-boxing","tag-individually-packaged-meals","tag-location-catering","tag-red-hot-box","tag-red-radish-hot-box"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Red Radish Hot Box Catering: Packaged meals and contactless food delivery service<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"We\u2019ve adapted to a new way of catering since COVID and now provide packaged meals and contactless hot box food delivery. Get in touch!\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/red-radish-hot-box-catering-packaged-meals-and-contactless-food-delive